2. Section 39.13 is amended by adding the following new airworthiness directive:





Israel Aircraft Industries Limited: 

Docket 94-NM-39-AD.






Applicability: 

Model 1125 Westwind Astra airplanes; serial numbers 004 through 066 inclusive, and 068; certificated in any category.




Compliance: 

