FIP proposal arose at least in part from a feeling in California that the emission regulation of certain sources was
not keeping pace with the attainment needs of California areas or with the stringency of control imposed on other sectors
of the California economy. For today's FIP proposal, EPA is proposing controls for these sources which include the
following provisions: 

