area-wide commercial aircraft emissions. If this total emissions 
quantity did not exceed the allowance for that year, airlines 
could operate undisturbed by the FIP. If the total actual 
emissions quantity did exceed a given year's allowance, however, 
the emissions fee system would be implemented for that year and 
would remain in effect for all subsequent years. 
