) Authority. EPA is proposing this South Coast emission averaging standard program under its broad remedial authority
under section 110(c). No provision of section 213, section 209, or any other sections of the Clean Air Act, clearly
prohibits EPA from exercising its section 110(c) in the manner proposed herein. 


