proposes that the manufacturer be allowed to offer the average 
retail value for the vehicle in question as specified in the NADA 
``Official Used Car Guide,'' if the manufacturers elects this 
option. One option would utilize the national ``Blue Book'' to 
avoid the possible effects of this program on ``Blue Book'' levels 
