manufacturers. EPA requests comment on requiring manufacturers 
to inform all vehicle owners, by letter, if the failure rate for 
the enhanced in-use I/M standards has exceeded the liability 
threshold. Such a letter would state that vehicle owner repair 
responsibility has ended and that the manufacturer is thereafter 
