Table of Standards, and not complying with that standard, shall not constitute a violation of paragraph (c)(2) of
this section until eighteen months after the effective date of the standard. 
(5) Sale or application of a coating in a container of one quart capacity or less shall not constitute a violation of
paragraph (c)(1) or (c)(2) of this section until January 1, 2003. 
(6) All VOC-containing materials shall be stored in closed containers when not in use. In use includes, but is not limited
