 A person or facility shall not 
apply a coating subject to this section except by means of the 
following application methods: 
(A) Electrostatic spray application; 
(B) Flow coat application; 
(C) Dip coat application; 
(D) Hand application methods; 
(E) High-volume low-pressure (HVLP) spray application; 
or 
