 means planned open burning of trash, leaves, 
and refuse from all activities except agricultural operations, 
forest management, range improvement, improvement of land for 
wildlife and game habitat, disease or pest prevention, operation 
or maintenance of a system for the delivery of water used in any 
agricultural operation, forest management, range improvement, 
land improvement for wildlife and game habitat, and disease or 
pest prevention operation, and wildland vegetation management 
