 means establish, development, care 
and reproduction of stands of timber. 


Timber operations

 means cutting or removal of timber or 
other forest vegetation. 


Waste burning

 means agricultural burning, range management 
burning, forest management burning, and open burning. 


Wildland vegetation management burning

