Personnel who perform emission inspections at 
each emission inspection station operated by the test provider(s) 
shall be certified by the Administrator as emission inspectors. 
The emission inspection shall only be performed by certified 
emission inspectors. 
(2) 

Certified emission inspector requirements. 

