desiring to be certified shall: 
(i) Be at least 18 years of age. 
(ii) Have completed an emission inspection training course, 
approved by the Administrator, that includes, at a minimum, 
information on the following: 
(A) The air pollution problem, including its cause and 
effects. 
(B) The purpose, function and goal of the inspection 
program. 
