the reasons therefore. Service of said notification may be made 
in person or by mail, and such service may be proved by the 
written acknowledgement of the persons served or affidavit of the 
person making the service. The permit shall be reinstated when 
the EPA is furnished with all requested information, analyses, 
plans, and specifications. 

